node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Scary Mommy on August 15, 2021 tagging @mamasgotproblems. May be an image of animal and text that says '3 year old orangutan goes "boneless" in an attempt to make it more difficult for his mom to remove him from the playground, and have never felt like I have more in common with an animal Mama than I do from this picture of her giving zero fucks and dragging him out anyway. @MamasGotProblems amasGotProblems'.

Photo by Scary Mommy on August 14, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Risa Hoshino, MD @risahoshinoMD I'm so tired of "experts" claiming that kids don't need to wear a mask in school. The politicization of public health is hurting innocent children. Us pediatricians & the AAP-the actual experts in kids' health-call fo universal masking NOW Children are deserving of protection.'.

node.text: Stop using our children as pawns in your twisted political games. (by @risahoshinoMD on Twitter)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Scary Mommy on August 14, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Moms get shit done. We handle our responsibilities and make sure everyone has what they need, exactly when they need it. But don't think that because we make miracles happen, we're not tired, struggling, and in need of help. Smomy'.

Photo by Scary Mommy on August 14, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'I think working mother is perhaps the most nonsensical concept ever concocted. I mean, who isn't a working mother? And then add a paid job to it, so what are you then? A working working mother? Imagine saying working father. -Rachel Yoder, NIGHTBITCH Scary M0 Mommy Book'.
